<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka gam lui ding ka chenna hi,
 Aw bangtik leh ka pawtsan dem?
 Angel vamhaw leh ka Lal mel chu,
 Muh kal ka ngaklah.

[V2]
 Aw, Jerusalem dai, ka Lalpa'n,
 Thawmhau in a ngak;
 Hansie dawl thingah a thawksak ui,
 A linglukhuk tawh.

[V3]
 2. Na thawk dan ka gen thiem thei puoi,
 Gitloh thawihnan van Belam No;
 Na hung pieng mun nuomlo Bethlehem,
 Bawng In tawm nuoi ah.

[V4]
 3. Lal Isu ka enchim thei puoi,
 Kalvari lam hunnga nang ie;
 Vannuoi gitloh puoa na thawkna,
 Ngilh ding guol ei puoi.</lyrics>
<title>Lal Isu Thawkna Leh Thihna</title>
<hymn_number>54</hymn_number>
</song>